    "Thus, the method samples according to a shape or the number of points.",
    "The method is called PointFlow, and it greatly utilizes the advantages of normalizing flows (Rezende and Mohamed 2015) in the VAE architecture.",
    "This method might not exceed the accuracy of state-of-the-art approaches, but it has great potential in the usage of image-based point cloud reconstructions.",
    "The problem of generating complex shapes is also addressed by Li et al. (2022b), who propose EditVAE, which introduces part awareness into the model, in other words, the object generation task is divided into the part generation task, where the parts are assembled following a schematic, and each part has its own disentangled latent representation, which also learns the dependencies between parts.",
